keyFacts: The document is a Google subscriber information record produced to the SDNY as part of the Epstein case.
It details a Google account (email: gmaxl/maxi) created on April 12, 2015, with last logins in October 2016.
The account was associated with numerous Google services including Gmail, Google Drive, Google Calendar, and Google Voice.
The file path suggests this document was part of a production from Google to legal authorities.
